Package: betticurves
Type: Package
Title: Compute Betti Curves in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rafael", "Gonzalez", email = "gonzalez.gouveia@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Rafael Gonzalez <gonzalez.gouveia@gmail.com>
Description: The betticurves packege implements betti curves from topological data analysis.
    It computes the curve based on a homology diagram. 
    It accepts diagrams from TDA packege and TDAstat packege.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
